Class ActiveMqSslJmsFactory

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JmsFactory, AutoCloseable
    public class ActiveMqSslJmsFactory
extends JndiJmsFactory
implements JmsFactory
    IMPORTANT: This is loaded and initialized via SPI. Make sure that an instance can be created even when required libraries are missing!
    This extends JndiJmsFactory for using JNDI when looking up queue/topic. Only obtaining a ConnectionFactory is different here.
